---
import TTELayout from '~/layouts/TTELayout.astro';
---

<TTELayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Top Tier Electrical"
  description="Privacy policy for Top Tier Electrical, including data collection, usage, retention, and contact details for West Michigan customers."
  canonical="https://toptier-electrical.com/privacy"
>
  <main id="main-content">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li aria-current="page">Privacy Policy</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p><em>Last updated: April 19, 2026</em></p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="container section-pad legal-content">
      <p>
        Top Tier Electrical respects your privacy. This page explains what we collect, why we collect it, and how to
        contact us with questions.
      </p>

      <h2>Who this policy applies to</h2>
      <p>This policy applies to visitors and customers using:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://toptier-electrical.com">https://toptier-electrical.com</a></li>
        <li>Contact, booking, and quote request forms hosted on this website</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact details you submit (name, phone, email, address, and project details)</li>
        <li>Appointment preferences and service request notes</li>
        <li>Basic technical and analytics data (pages viewed, browser/device type, referring source)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do <strong>not</strong> intentionally collect sensitive personal information unless you include it in a message.
      </p>

      <h2>How we use information</h2>
      <p>We use your information to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Respond to your inquiry or quote request</li>
        <li>Schedule and provide electrical services</li>
        <li>Send service-related communications (confirmation, follow-up, scheduling changes)</li>
        <li>Improve website performance, content quality, and user experience</li>
        <li>Maintain security and prevent spam or abuse</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Form processing and service providers</h2>
      <p>
        We use third-party tools to operate this website and process forms/analytics. Those providers process data on
        our behalf only as needed to deliver their services.
      </p>
      <p>Examples include hosting, form handling, and analytics providers.</p>

      <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
      <p>This website may use cookies or similar technologies for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Essential site functionality</li>
        <li>Measuring page performance and traffic patterns</li>
        <li>Improving content relevance and call-to-action clarity</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>We retain inquiry and customer records only as long as reasonably necessary for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Customer support and service delivery</li>
        <li>Legal, accounting, and operational requirements</li>
      </ul>
      <p>When no longer needed, data is deleted or anonymized where practical.</p>

      <h2>Sharing of information</h2>
      <p>We do not sell personal information.</p>
      <p>We may share information only when necessary to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Deliver requested services</li>
        <li>Work with trusted service providers</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations or enforce our rights</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <p>You may request to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access or correct your information</li>
        <li>Ask us to delete information we are not required to keep</li>
        <li>Opt out of non-essential communications</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This website is not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from
        children under 13.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. Changes are posted on this page with a revised "Last updated" date.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact us</h2>
      <p>For privacy questions or requests, contact:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@toptier-electrical.com">info@toptier-electrical.com</a></li>
        <li><strong>Phone/Text:</strong> <a href="tel:+16163347159">(616) 334-7159</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</TTELayout>
